'''1. MHK Košice''' is the [[Team handball|handball]] team from Slovakia. Košice won [[Slovenská hadzanárska extraliga|National Championship of Slovakia]] twice, in 1997 and 1999.
==Accomplishments== *'''[[Slovenská hadzanárska extraliga|National Championship of Slovakia]]:''' 2 **1997, 1999 *'''[[National Cup of Slovakia]]:''' 9 **1979, 1980, 1983, 1992, 1995, 1996, 1998, 1999, 2003
