'''84th Anniversary Bang Bon Stadium''' or '''Chalerm Phrakiat Bang Bon Stadium''' ({{lang-th| สนามกีฬาเฉลิมพระเกียรติ 84 พรรษา บางบอน}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Bang Bon District]], [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]].  The stadium built for celebration of the 84th Birthday Anniversary of King [[Bhumibol Adulyadej]], hence the name of the venue. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. The stadium holds 5,000 people.<ref>https://www.timeout.com/bangkok/th/news/%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B5%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A8%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B8%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%B4%E0%B9%8C%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%8A%E0%B8%B8%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%94-%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%93%E0%B8%B0%E0%B9%81%E0%B8%AB%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%8A%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B8%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%9E%E0%B8%AF-010818</ref>

