The '''Andorran Sailing Federation''' (Catalan: ''{{lang|ca|Federació Andorrana De Vela, FAV}}'') is the national governing body for the sport of sailing in [[Andorra]], recognised by the [[International Sailing Federation]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sailing.org/about-isaf/mna/andorra.php |accessdate=May 1, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120507122006/http://www.sailing.org/about-isaf/mna/andorra.php |archivedate=May 7, 2012 }}</ref>
