{{Infobox football club | clubname = Costa del Este FC | image = Costa del Este FC.png | image_size = | upright = | alt = | caption = | fullname = Costa del Este Futbol Club | nickname = | short name = | founded = 2008 (as Santos FC) | dissolved = afas | American = | ground = <!-- or: stadium --> | capacity = 8000 | owntitle = <!--optional, default: Owner --> | owner = | chrtitle = <!--optional, default: Chairman --> | chairman = | mgrtitle = <!--optional, default: Manager --> | manager = | coach = | league = Liga Nacional de Ascenso | season = | position = | website = http://www.costadelestefc.com | kit_alt1 = | pattern_la1 = | pattern_b1 = | pattern_ra1 = | pattern_sh1 = | pattern_so1 = | leftarm1 = | body1 = | rightarm1 = | shorts1 = | socks1 = | pattern_name1 = <!--optional, default: Home colours --> | kit_alt2 = | pattern_la2 = | pattern_b2 = | pattern_ra2 = | pattern_sh2 = | pattern_so2 = | leftarm2 = | body2 = | rightarm2 = | shorts2 = | socks2 = | pattern_name2 = <!--optional, default: Away colours --> | kit_alt3 = | pattern_la3 = | pattern_b3 = | pattern_ra3 = | pattern_sh3 = | pattern_so3 = | leftarm3 = | body3 = | rightarm3 = | shorts3 = | socks3 = | pattern_name3 = <!--optional, default: Third colours --> | current = }}
'''Costa del Este''' is a [[Panama]]nian [[association football|football club]].
The club is based in Panama City and takes its name from the [[Costa del Este (Panama City)|real estate development]] in the township of Juan Díaz, Panama City. Since its inception in 2008 and until 2014, the club was based in [[La Chorrera, Panama|La Chorrera]] and known as Santos FC.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Onda|first1=Canal de Cable|title=Costa del Este FC debuta en la LNA con triunfo ante Deportivo Vista Alegre|url=http://www.cableondasports.com/futbol/nacional/lna/costa-del-este-fc-debuta-en-la-lna-con-triunfo-ante-deportivo-vista-alegre/|website=Cable Onda Sports|accessdate=18 April 2017|language=en|date=24 January 2014}}</ref>
==Achievements==
* [[Liga Nacional de Ascenso]] winner: ** [[2015–16 Liga Nacional de Ascenso|2016 Apertura]] *[[Copa Rommel Fernández]] winner: ** [[2012 Copa Rommel Fernández|2012]] (as Santos FC)<ref>{{cite web|title=Santos se corona campeón de la Copa Rommel 2012 {{!}} PanamaFutbol.com|url=http://panamafutbol.com/?p=8416|website=panamafutbol.com|accessdate=18 April 2017}}</ref>
