658 "Gold for Korea, Silver for China and Bronze for Chinese Taipei"]. RANKA online</ref> | [[Changhun Kim]] ({{KOR}}) | [[Aohua Hu]] ({{CHN}}) | [[Jyun-Fu Lai]] ({{TPE}}) |}
